mārgam api kathayet. āstāṃ tāvat sagauravaṃ vastu.

<commentary>lokāprasādanivāraṇāyāha.

na bhujam utkṣipya kaṃcid āhvayet, alpaprayojanatāratamye. mahati punar adoṣaḥ. acchaṭādiśabdaṃ tu kuryāt. tadakaraṇe 'samāhitacāritāyām asaṃvṛtaḥ syāt. etāvatā auddhatyaparihāro 'pi darśito bhavati.</commentary>

sa hi śayyāṃ parikalpayannevaṃ parikalpayedityupadarśayannāha-

bhagavato mahānirvāṇaśayyām iva śayyāṃ parikalpayet. abhimatayā diśā śiro vidhāya, dakṣiṇena pārśvena, pādasyopari pādam ādhāya, dakṣiṇaṃ bāhum upadhānaṃ kṛtvā, vāmaṃ ca prasārya jaṅghopari niveśya, cīvaraiḥ susaṃvṛtakāyaḥ, smṛtaḥ, saṃprajānānaḥ, utthānasaṃjñī, ālokasaṃjñī, śayitaḥ, nācittakamiddhāvaṣṭabdhaḥ. na ca nidrāsukham ākhādayet, na ca pārśvasukham anyatra yāvad evaiṣāṃ mahābhūtānāṃ sthitaye yāpanāyai iti.